io.werval.spi.http

Interface HttpBuildersSPI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HttpBuilders
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    WervalTestSupport
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CacheTest, TemplatesTest, WervalRule, WervalTest 

    public interface HttpBuildersSPI
extends HttpBuilders
    HTTP API Objects Builders SPI.

    Use this to create instances of HTTP API Objects found in the io.werval.api.http package.

    Typically used in unit tests running an Application.

    All builders are immutable and reusable.
